     H            Y.
     F** UTLR02B ********************************************
     F*  GET YYYYMM(N+1) AND YYYYMM(N+2) FROM YYYYMM(N)
     F*  COPIED FROM ABBRSD                                 *
     F*-----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR02B'
     F*                    PARM           P@N0    6        N
     F*                    PARM           P@N1    6        N+1
     F*                    PARM           P@N2    6        N+2
     F*  IN   P@N0  :  6A DATE1 (YYYYMM)
     F*  OUT  P@N1  :  6A NEXT MONTH OF P@N0
     F*       P@N2  :  6A NEXT MONTH OF P@N01
     F*******************************************************
      * DATE6
     I            DS
     I                                        1   6 WKYMD6
     I                                        1   4 WKYM
     I                                        5   6 WKDD
      * DATE8
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80W$YMD
     I                                        1   60W$YM
     I                                        1   40W$YY
     I                                        5   60W$MM
     I                                        7   80W$DD
     C*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@N0    6        N
     C                     PARM           P@N1    6        N+1
     C                     PARM           P@N2    6        N+2
      *
     C                     MOVELP@N0      WKYMD8  8
     C                     MOVE '01'      WKYMD8
     C*
     C                     MOVE WKYMD8    W$YMD
     C                     Z-ADDW$YM      $$N     60       N+0
     C*
     C                     ADD  1         W$MM
     C           W$MM      IFGT 12
     C                     Z-ADD1         W$MM
     C                     ADD  1         W$YY
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     Z-ADDW$YM      $$N1    60
     C                     MOVE $$N1      P@N1              N+1
     C*
     C                     ADD  1         W$MM
     C           W$MM      IFGT 12
     C                     Z-ADD1         W$MM
     C                     ADD  1         W$YY
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     Z-ADDW$YM      $$N2    60
     C                     MOVE $$N2      P@N2              N+2
     C*
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
